{"tid":1242474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友寫既數碼安全指引","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:46:16.000Z","uid":74182,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15f3e81e503624763c2e91ed5284b71852469d17","tid":1242474,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"我個TECH朋友上個禮拜寫左呢個非常簡單直接既數碼安全指引 (Digital Safety Guideline)。黎緊監控只會越來越全面，我地一定要加強保護自己既身份同私隱。<br />\n<br />\n尤其係週四五會去發夢既朋友, 請你出門口發夢前花D時間睇下! 保護自己！！！！<br />\n<br />\nMy tech friends made this really simple and direct Digital Safety Guideline last week. It&rsquo;s practical and useful. Even though not all of us are front-line protesters/ human rights defenders, I suggest we all take extra steps to protect our privacy because surveillance will only become more all-encompassing. （You can find the link to the English version in the doc）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cryptpad.fr/pad/#/2/pad/view/tLA6A6v+G8ZeQHZQ-TmVFDvP5XjcQVVGB29YDquhWYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcryptpad.fr%2Fpad%2F%23%2F2%2Fpad%2Fview%2FtLA6A6v%2BG8ZeQHZQ-TmVFDvP5XjcQVVGB29YDquhWYI%2F&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=3f04223c\" target=\"_blank\">https://cryptpad.fr/pad/#/2/pad/view/tLA6A6v+G8ZeQHZQ-TmVFDvP5XjcQVVGB29YDquhWYI/</a>"},{"pid":"9c737e560f6ab67b5e5e3308244b83bf4fbee5e2","tid":1242474,"uid":239674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"寫得幾好 幾有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別係10位密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你的朋友就是...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2459fb765771cc0a022896f09984729b1e7851","tid":1242474,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c737e560f6ab67b5e5e3308244b83bf4fbee5e2","tid":1242474,"uid":239674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"寫得